{"tid":1476770,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"明玩野？荃灣映日灣對面街最新成交12600蚊呎","createTime":"2019-08-16T02:22:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T07:11:15.000Z","uid":10014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3c4b6f436fc137ead02f3e736f6fe991a63f7e8f","tid":1476770,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:22:23.000Z","msg":"康睦庭園單位減180萬易手 <br />\n荃灣區亦出現業主大劈價求售個案。中原地產程尚傑表示，荃灣康睦庭園第2座中層B室，實用面積634平方呎，三房間隔，原叫價980萬元，業主眼見本港局勢及中美貿易戰惡化，市場氣氛非常低落，加上區內新盤低開促銷，令二手市況進一步受壓，前兩天裂口式降價100萬元至880萬元，立即引起一名區內換樓客的興趣，買家還價至800萬元，業主亦爽快答應再減價80萬元，以800萬元沽出單位，實用呎價12,618元，累減180萬元，減幅達18%。 "},{"pid":"d872eac06d0b560ba7038561577113577c65be12","tid":1476770,"uid":15605,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:43:26.000Z","msg":"住荃灣，有錢買樓冇命住"},{"pid":"d498b8bab3b1012812444df160dde8dbe3b164d3","tid":1476770,"uid":270661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"同類型單位對上2月成交771萬，邊有跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2810e1941625dcf82a48770ea54c5624aa072dc","tid":1476770,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d498b8bab3b1012812444df160dde8dbe3b164d3","tid":1476770,"uid":270661,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:44:36.000Z","msg":"同類型單位對上2月成交771萬，邊有跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:51:40.000Z","msg":"呢D超少伙數 冇投資客.."},{"pid":"fc85fe090e19d8cbef64d309c666f035ff1d997e","tid":1476770,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"樓爆 啪啪啪<br />\n低置 啪啪啪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ef809cf20c6c5ec6462a342141c7d5a6a59897","tid":1476770,"uid":90946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T03:47:55.000Z","msg":"隔兩條街二陂坊<br />\n用生命黎居住架"},{"pid":"5b2d5e711e81fd8efa52d5e1aa668bade70b5a90","tid":1476770,"uid":276273,